<!-- Container (The Band Section) -->
<div id="band" class="container text-center">
    <h3>FIRE LOCATOR SYSTEM</h3>
    <p style="font-family:'Century Gothic'; line-height:24px; font-size:17px"><em>Fast Services</em></p>
    <p style="font-family:'Century Gothic'; line-height:27px; font-size:15px">To create an early fire detection system capable of detecting municipal circumstances and quickly alerting the fire service to the incident's location. This study made use of developmental research and the Arduino Uno. This system will give everyone an early warning while also ensuring that no alarm goes unnoticed or neglected and that immediate action is taken. The developers came up with the idea of developing a system that would enable firefighters respond faster in an emergency and reduce the time it takes to notify the fire department about fires in Taguig City. The internet will make communication between a homeowner and the fire department much easier. The internet-connected fire alarm was connected to the fire department's control room, which provided the data that would be sent via the internet.</p>
    <br>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-4">
            <p class="text-center"  style="font-family:'Century Gothic';font-size:16px;"><strong>Fire Detector</strong></p><br>
